Dialogue: 100,0:00:06.95,0:00:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ciclopul către supervizorul unu:
Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.84,0:00:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Au ajuns deja la vechiul terminal de tranzit de mare viteză din punctul 122.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.18,0:00:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Scuze, radarele noastre erau bruiate și nu am reușit să-i detectăm până în ultimul moment.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.59,0:00:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Asta va fi o luptă grea pentru nou-veniți.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.96,0:00:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ce plan ai?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.29,0:00:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mergeți cu toții în punctul 062
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.19,0:00:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,și trimiteți o unitate ca să le ademenească.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.28,0:00:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Asta îi va aduce în fața altileriei rămase.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.73,0:00:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Deci ne vom lupta cu ei fix înaintea de bazei noastre, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.10,0:00:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dacă vor trece de noi, tot ce va rămâne sunt minele și artileria ca să-i oprească, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.78,0:00:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Așa este, dar dacă vrem să supraviețuim, asta e cea mai bună variantă.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.29,0:00:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Bine, Maiestate!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.93,0:00:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for today's update on the war \Nfrom San Magnolia Military HQ!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.16,0:01:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The pride of our nation, the Juggernaut, has intercepted
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.85,0:01:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and decimated their forces causing them to withdraw.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.71,0:01:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Defending the nation with our\Nadvanced and ethical drones,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.99,0:01:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,has resulted in zero Republic casualties!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.68,0:01:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The day when the righteousness of our nation smashes the evil remnants of the wicked Empire is not far off!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.80,0:01:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All hail the Republic of San Magnolia!\NGlory to the five-colored flag!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:26.48,0:01:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hei, este prințesa distrugătoare de păpuși!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:30.37,0:01:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Am auzit că ai reușit să învingi Legiunea și astăzi,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.29,0:01:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,o victorie pătată de sângele acelor porci.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.14,0:01:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,De asta e cunoscută drept Regina Pătată de Sânge sau Regina Sângeroasă!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:40.00,0:01:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai găsit care este diferența între oameni și porci?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.09,0:01:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Vai, are mereu aceeași expresie.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.91,0:01:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,La ce naiba se gândește?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.96,0:01:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A fost retrogradată pentru acei porci...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Și poartă o uniformă neagră când nimeni altcineva nu o face...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.46,0:01:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Legiunea nu va mai exista în doi ani!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.67,0:02:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Vine dintr-o familie faimoasă și bogată, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.67,0:02:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dacă s-ar comporta cum trebuie, ar avea o viață foarte ușoară.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.12,0:02:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,'Neața.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.48,0:02:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,'Neața.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.97,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,În legătură cu lucrul despre care mă întrebasei, vreau mai întâi să mă asigur de ceva.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.55,0:02:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Setările suplimentare ale dispozitivului RAID.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.94,0:02:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Foarte bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.35,0:02:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Voi ajunge acolo în două ore.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bine, ne vedem acolo.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:28.12,0:02:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,De câte ori trebuie să-ți spun, căpitan Milizé?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.38,0:02:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Folosirea neautorizată a artileriei, trimiterea de provizii neplanificate
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.46,0:02:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,și trimiterea de ordine către unități care nu sunt sub comanda ta.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.52,0:02:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai idee câte plângeri primesc?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.61,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nu-mi da mai multă muncă doar de dragul acelor rezidenți ai Distructului 86.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.81,0:02:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dacă mi-ai dat permisiunea anticipat,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.89,0:02:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,nu ai fi nevoit să te confrunți cu asemenea lucruri, locotenent-colonel.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.89,0:02:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ce vrei să spui?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.12,0:02:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tu și ceilalți vă puteți plânge cât doriți,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,dar nu o să-mi peste câtuși de puțin de ceea ce spuneți.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemernico!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cunoaște-ți locul! Ești doar un căpitan!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:06.52,0:03:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ești sigur că vrei asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.31,0:03:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Realizările tale sunt bazate pe performanțele subordonaților tăi.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.87,0:03:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.22,0:03:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu am cele mai bune performanțe dintre toți supervizorii.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.54,0:03:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dacă voi începe să distrug mai puține unități ale Legiunii și promovarea ta va fi afectată.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.90,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai grijă cum vorbești, căpitane.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Scuză-mă, locotenent-colonel.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.18,0:04:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Te voi lăsa pe tine să te ocupi de provizii.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.66,0:04:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.69,0:04:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, am verificat artileria zonei de luptă a Districtului 8 din regiunea sudică.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Exact cum ne așteptam, doar douăzeci la sută mai sunt funcționale.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nu mă surprinde.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Iar rata de uzură de pe câmpul de luptă...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.65,0:04:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hei, priviți!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Priviți! Ninge!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.64,0:04:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiar a venit iarna, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.36,0:04:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ciclopul către supervizorul prim:
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mă recepționezi?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.33,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Da. Ce este?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Am dat peste o formație inamică în timp ce patrulam.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Avem nevoie de ordinele tale.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Am înțeles.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.42,0:04:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Vă rog să continuați investigația.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.65,0:04:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ciclopule, raportează situația.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Îmi cer scuze că am întârziat.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai venit destul de devreme, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.73,0:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Haide să ne vedem de discuția noastră, Lena.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.07,0:05:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.97,0:05:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Am înțeles. Mulțumesc pentru raport.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.31,0:05:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Desigur. Voi aștepta aproximările tale în ceea ce privește puterea Legiunii, Maiestate.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, mă voi strădui.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.71,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's both work together to do our best.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.15,0:05:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Desigur.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.95,0:05:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Doar ești supervizorul nostru. Ne bazăm pe tine.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.73,0:05:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Și eu mă bazez pe voi.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.98,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Am nevoie de informațiile tale de pe câmpul de luptă, Ciclopule.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.65,0:05:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Știi, nu ar fi momentul să-mi folosești numele adevărat?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.02,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dacă nu intenționezi să o faci, atunci de ce ne-ai mai întrebat?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.58,0:06:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Deoarece...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.90,0:06:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,asta e responsabilitatea mea ca supervizor.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.23,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mereu ești așa serioasă și formală, știi?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Crezi ce dorești.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.67,0:06:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Totuși, mulțumită ție vom reuși să trăim puțin mai mult.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.85,0:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Apreciez efortul, dar vom ajunge în escadronul Vârf de Lance în câteva luni.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.11,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Cel mai puternic tip pe care-l știu a fost trimis în misiunea specială de recunoaștere acum ceva timp.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:37.80,0:06:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Probabil e mort acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.80,0:06:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Decapitatul zeu al morții care-și prefera mereu lamele.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:48.21,0:06:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Care crezi că va avea loc primul? Misiunea noastră de recunoaștere sau atacul Legiunii?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.40,0:06:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nu știu.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.06,0:07:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dar treaba mea acum este să vă pregătesc pentru marele atac al Legiunii, care va veni.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.78,0:07:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,M-am hotărât deja să vă ajut, dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,în cele din urmă, nu contează.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Și o vei face indiferent?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.01,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dar, Ciclopule, nu uita să-mi trimiți raportul patrulării.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Recepționat!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.50,0:07:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,În orice caz, mi-au spus să supraviețuiesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.21,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Au crezut în mine și mi-au spus să lupt și să supraviețuiesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.74,0:07:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To live up to the hopes of those\Nwho are no longer with us...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu doar până aici pot merge.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.01,0:08:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go the rest of the way yourself, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai camarazi alături de tine acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.07,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiar ai crescut.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.93,0:08:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nu lăsa ca amintirea mea să te tragă în jos.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.20,0:08:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mă poți uita.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.02,0:08:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,De fapt...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.68,0:09:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Vreau să-ți amintești de mine, din când în când.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.60,0:09:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Trăiește liber și găsește-ți fericirea...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Și din când în când, știi?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Doar din când în când.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.73,0:09:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai grijă de tine.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.29,0:09:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Și găsește-ți fericirea.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.41,0:09:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Frate!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.04,0:10:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware, it'll just be a few words.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You've just woken up?\NGreetings.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.92,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To start, would you please tell me your name?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.28,0:10:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the generals are really cautious\Nand forced me to wear this hazmat suit.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.62,0:10:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is no way to greet someone, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.55,0:10:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ernst.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And yours?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.41,0:10:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinei Nouzen.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.54,0:10:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Federal Republic of Giad!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.14,0:10:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Giad"?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:54.02,0:10:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I should explain.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.41,0:11:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empire of Giad that created the Legion was\Noverthrown and reformed into a Federal Republic.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.33,0:11:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, we're also fighting\Nthe remaining Legion, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:08.08,0:11:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When we found you, you were captured\Nby the Legion on our western front.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you'd be worried.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:24.79,0:11:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sleeping so we turned the windows opaque.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:32.37,0:11:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still not sure\Nwhat happened before we found you.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do happen to remember anything...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:40.31,0:11:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! That's enough for now.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:43.74,0:11:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:45.16,0:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The scary lady's going to get mad at me, \Nso I'll be going.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.03,0:11:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But remember this.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:50.89,0:11:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first foreign visitors we've had \Nsince our nation's founding.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:56.29,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And we were too busy fighting the Legion\Nso we don't have any procedures in place for this.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry, we will not harm you.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:05.25,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ernst Zimerman,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:09.40,0:12:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the provisional President of the Federal Republic of Giad.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What does our analysis show?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:16.53,0:12:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe to say they aren't agents \Nof San Magnolia or any other country.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about them being a new Legion type
Dialogue: 100,0:12:24.62,0:12:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or carrying a new type of Legion bioweapon?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:28.38,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Our initial scans and test shows no abnormalities.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Legion unit that captured them?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:34.84,0:12:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an older model, but is undoubtedly a Dinosauria.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:39.49,0:12:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And the object attached to their ears?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:43.00,0:12:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They stated it was a communication device.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:46.32,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It creates a mental link between devices\Nand is reminiscent of that certain family's ability.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How revolutionary.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:52.86,0:12:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The safest option for the Federacy\Nwould be to eliminate them
Dialogue: 100,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:06.29,0:13:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you were out for three whole days.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:08.86,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, Kurena was bawling her eyes out.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:12.60,0:13:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was not!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:15.73,0:13:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin, I know now's not a good time,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.56,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'd better ready yourself once you're better.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we all feel the same way.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:28.37,0:13:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever pull that shit again,\NI will kick your ass.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to die—
Dialogue: 100,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to make me mad.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:36.41,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you didn't mean to die,\Nyou knew it'd probably happen if you went out there.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:41.81,0:13:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we've all been in that position at least once...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's why we can't forgive it!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we understand!\NIt's not fair.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:51.17,0:13:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Never do that again!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:53.59,0:13:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so worried!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:04.93,0:14:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But who knows what happens now...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:13.05,0:14:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So yeah, starting from today,\Nyou're all citizens of the Federacy!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:22.52,0:14:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen you for a month, \Nand the first thing you say is "So yeah"?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.34,0:14:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you want to make a bunch of strange kids \Nwho were kicked out of their old country into citizens?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.29,0:14:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be safer just to kill us?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:41.43,0:14:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What benefit do you get from saving us?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:44.52,0:14:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A society that refuses to save children \Nbecause there's no "benefit"
Dialogue: 100,0:14:49.75,0:14:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is a society that benefits no one.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:52.59,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And if humanity can't survive without\Nkilling children because they're "strange,"
Dialogue: 100,0:15:00.18,0:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,then humanity doesn't deserve to survive.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:08.32,0:15:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll be assuming the role\Nof your guardian for a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:12.76,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So rest a bit and see this country for yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can decide what you want to do.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:28.10,0:15:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The war machines we recovered, the "Juggernauts..."
Dialogue: 100,0:15:31.50,0:15:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Capabilities aside, their combat logs are amazing.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to speak with them.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:37.46,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're already involved with them.\NWe won't let you have them.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:42.01,0:15:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,High-mobility combat data and the personnel who generatepd that data.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a perfect fit to operate my prototypes.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:49.16,0:15:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd be wasted on those slow Vánagandr.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:51.62,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say, spider woman?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say, beetle?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all free to speak with them.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:57.57,0:15:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't let them be operators.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:59.81,0:16:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we did, we'd be no different from the Republic.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:02.17,0:16:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're all saying in their counseling sessions
Dialogue: 100,0:16:04.60,0:16:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that they want to go back to the battlefield.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:08.97,0:16:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because the battlefield\N is all they know right now.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:14.92,0:16:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Actions should be met with rewards.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:17.72,0:16:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they've fought for so long,\Nthey should be offered a chance at peace.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially since their homeland refused to do it.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:28.03,0:16:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the Federacy to be just, at least.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:31.21,0:16:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:33.41,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the ideal of mankind.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us save our pitiful comrades!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:05.91,0:17:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's save them!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:07.69,0:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eighty-Six are victims!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Victims!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:12.32,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us save our pitiful comrades!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:15.19,0:17:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's save them!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:15.18,0:17:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all happy when you were rescued,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:20.23,0:17:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because they've finally learned\Nthat another country had survived.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:24.86,0:17:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But when they learned how you were treated,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:27.81,0:17:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,they became overcome with the desire \Nto save you and your comrades.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.15,0:17:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my house, but from now on it's your home.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Welcome!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.27,0:17:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Push that desk!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:49.92,0:17:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:54.92,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, poor souls who were banished \Nfrom your country!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:02.53,0:18:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The great Giad welcomes you with pity and compassion!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:07.45,0:18:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't expect any kind of recompense \Nfrom low-borns like you,
Dialogue: 100,0:18:10.37,0:18:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so your thanks are enough!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:14.17,0:18:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, red-eyes!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking away?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought there might be someone else here.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:19.41,0:18:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You already shut the door!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:23.33,0:18:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:25.23,0:18:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the problem with low-born people \Nfrom the Republic.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:28.31,0:18:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your daughter?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.38,0:18:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be rude of me to say it but\Nyou probably need to discipline her better.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:32.92,0:18:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. \NShe's not my daughter.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:35.72,0:18:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you really think I'm the daughter \Nof this lowly bureaucrat?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm—
Dialogue: 100,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Frederica Rosenfort.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:41.95,0:18:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things happened, and now she's staying here.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:48.90,0:18:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's annoying to explain to everyone,
Dialogue: 100,0:18:51.85,0:18:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so officially speaking she's my daughter.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:54.94,0:18:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But regardless, you'll be living together for a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:59.01,0:19:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd appreciate it if you'd think of her \Nas a slightly naïve little sister.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:05.90,0:19:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Little sister," huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:07.27,0:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, on paper I've also adopted you all too.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:12.08,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can call me "Dad," if you want.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just joking.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:28.51,0:19:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that on your neck?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that Frederica.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already explained their situation.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:36.98,0:19:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You also have wounds you'd like to keep to yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:44.58,0:19:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the cute little sister \Nyou've been given to heal your wounds.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:50.10,0:19:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The family and home and happiness you lost...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:53.86,0:19:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The noble and compassionate \NFederacy is willing to give you.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:58.33,0:20:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Be very nice to me!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:01.43,0:20:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brothers and sisters!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:05.81,0:20:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Theresa, they're being mean!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:09.82,0:20:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:10.98,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Frederica, everything that just happened \Nwas your own fault.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Was not! Was not!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:17.64,0:20:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sunt Theresa. Voi avea grijă de voi.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:24.16,0:20:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, everyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bored.\NThey all went to sleep so early.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I know you're tired.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was holding on to this.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:45.94,0:20:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in your war machine.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:48.75,0:20:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it yours?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:54.87,0:20:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:59.31,0:21:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Theresa.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, sir.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:03.44,0:21:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids that age eat a lot. \NIt's fun to cook for them.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:08.38,0:21:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. \NThis is likely to be difficult.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:12.32,0:21:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. \NServing you is my job.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:19.80,0:21:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you despise me for trying to\Ncompensate for things like this?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:26.82,0:21:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm using them as replacements?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:29.75,0:21:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No. They could never replace them.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:33.66,0:21:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Every person is their own, \Nirreplaceable individual.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:39.44,0:21:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, people try to bury the past.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:43.48,0:21:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In whatever way they can.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whom are you talking to,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:58.82,0:21:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiri...
Dialogue: 100,0:23:36.25,0:23:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
